AT.name: Warriors Orochi 3 Hyper
AT.description: Warriors Orochi 3 Hyper vereint die beliebten Helden der Serien Dynasty Warriors und Samurai Warriors in einer Geschichte, die auch noch Charaktere von Ninja Gaiden, Warriors: Legends of Troy, Bladestorm, Trinity: Souls of Zill O'll und Dead or Alive einbindet sowie einen neuen, speziell für Warriors Orochi 3 Hyper erschaffenen Charakter vorstellt.

AU.name: Warriors Orochi 3 Hyper
AU.description: Warriors Orochi 3 Hyper combines the much loved heroes of the Dynasty Warriors and Samurai Warriors series in a story that also features characters from Ninja Gaiden, Warriors: Legends of Troy, Bladestorm, Trinity: Souls of Zill O’ll, Dead or Alive and a new character made specifically for Warriors Orochi 3 Hyper! Years after the battle against Orochi, the Serpent King, the heroes of the Three Kingdoms and the Warring States struggle to seize control of the new universe they were thrown into when a new threat arises. A terrible and colossal monster, resembling a serpent with eight heads, casts its shadow across the land and defeats most of the brave warriors. The ones that survived, assisted by the mysterious Kaguya, travel back through time to save fallen warriors and forge new alliances, collect powerful weapons and build an army so they can have a chance to defeat the terrible Hydra.
